1
00:00:00,667 --> 00:00:01,500
- [GUN COCKS]
- [GUNSHOT]

2
00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:03,000
<i> I killed them both!</i>

3
00:00:03,533 --> 00:00:05,067
<i> Sandro, you bastard!</i>

4
00:00:05,733 --> 00:00:07,300
[SCREAMS]

5
00:00:07,300 --> 00:00:08,400
<i> Help!</i>

6
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,167
<i> Monette has been found.</i>

7
00:00:10,433 --> 00:00:11,633
<i> She was by the mangroves.</i>

8
00:00:13,267 --> 00:00:14,500
<i> Monette is dead.</i>

9
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:16,967
<i> No...</i>

10
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:20,367
I'm not doubting your abilities,

11
00:00:20,367 --> 00:00:23,367
<i>but how many more people
should die before this all ends?</i>

12
00:00:23,367 --> 00:00:26,267
<i>You're under arrest
on charges of conspiracy,</i>

13
00:00:26,267 --> 00:00:28,400
<i>bribery,
and obstruction of justice.</i>

14
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,133
<i> You betrayed me.</i>

15
00:00:30,133 --> 00:00:32,300
<i>From now on,
forget I'm even alive.</i>

16
00:00:32,567 --> 00:00:35,200
<i>We're going back
to the original plan.</i>

17
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:36,600
<i> I know you have a map,</i>

18
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:38,400
<i>and the rest are
with Michael's children.</i>

19
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,133
<i> Once we get all the maps,</i>

20
00:00:40,133 --> 00:00:42,267
<i> we will be unstoppable.</i>

21
00:00:42,267 --> 00:00:45,400
<i>I shouldn't have given you
that map from Sandro's house.</i>

22
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:47,567
<i>I don't have it anymore.
I gave it to Kiko.</i>

23
00:00:47,567 --> 00:00:48,767
<i> Just ask Trixie.</i>

24
00:00:48,767 --> 00:00:51,267
<i>Kiko has the map and
the brothers will look at it.</i>

25
00:00:51,267 --> 00:00:55,200
<i> Kiko, you have my map.</i>

26
00:00:56,500 --> 00:00:59,267
Justin, we just wanted to help.

27
00:01:00,633 --> 00:01:01,767
I know that.

28
00:01:02,167 --> 00:01:04,733
Alright, then
why won't you let us help?

29
00:01:05,633 --> 00:01:07,700
Do you know what it feels like
to be here,

30
00:01:07,733 --> 00:01:10,067
but we can't do
anything to help?

31
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:12,233
We've been through this
before, Justin.

32
00:01:12,233 --> 00:01:13,600
Just trust us.

33
00:01:15,133 --> 00:01:17,367
I just don't want anything bad
to happen to you.

34
00:01:18,733 --> 00:01:20,633
You're both important to me.

35
00:01:20,633 --> 00:01:23,500
I won't forgive myself
if you get in danger, too.

36
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:26,200
We won't get in danger,
I promise.

37
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,500
[GRUNTING]

38
00:01:28,733 --> 00:01:31,733
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

39
00:01:35,767 --> 00:01:37,733
[CHAIN RATTLING]

40
00:01:38,533 --> 00:01:41,633
[STRAINING]

41
00:01:45,833 --> 00:01:48,533
Let's just go. Come on.

42
00:01:49,467 --> 00:01:51,533
[STRAINING]

43
00:01:53,667 --> 00:01:56,767
[GRUNTING LOUDLY]

44
00:01:56,767 --> 00:01:58,200
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

45
00:02:00,733 --> 00:02:01,767
[METAL CLANGS]

46
00:02:02,300 --> 00:02:04,167
[GROANS]

47
00:02:06,767 --> 00:02:12,767
[DARK MUSIC CONTINUES]

48
00:02:12,767 --> 00:02:15,733
[CHAIN RATTLING]

49
00:02:22,467 --> 00:02:25,300
[MUSIC TURNS SUSPENSEFUL]

50
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:27,233
[GROANS LOUDLY]

51
00:02:27,233 --> 00:02:29,767
[BREATHES HEAVILY]

52
00:02:32,267 --> 00:02:34,767
[GRUNTING]

53
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:44,767
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

54
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:39,767
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

55
00:03:39,767 --> 00:03:40,733
[GRUNTS]

56
00:03:40,967 --> 00:03:42,800
[BREATHES HEAVILY]

57
00:03:43,533 --> 00:03:45,433
[CHAIN RATTLING]

58
00:03:52,667 --> 00:03:55,200
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

59
00:03:55,833 --> 00:04:02,767
[DARK MUSIC CONTINUES]

60
00:04:11,467 --> 00:04:12,500
Ah!

61
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:15,833
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

62
00:04:21,633 --> 00:04:22,867
- [METAL CLANGS]
- [SCREAMS]

63
00:04:33,833 --> 00:04:40,767
[DARK MUSIC CONTINUES]

64
00:04:58,267 --> 00:05:00,800
Looks like it's my lucky day.

65
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,300
I just saw your message.

66
00:05:11,733 --> 00:05:13,367
Yeah, I'm with them.

67
00:05:13,367 --> 00:05:14,533
We're on our way back.

68
00:05:14,867 --> 00:05:16,467
Alright.

69
00:05:16,467 --> 00:05:17,800
Thank you, Justin.

70
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,367
See you at the hotel.

71
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:26,767
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

72
00:05:28,333 --> 00:05:30,667
[BREATHES HEAVILY, GRUNTS]

73
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,400
- [GRUNTS LOUDLY]
- [METAL CLANGS]

74
00:05:40,333 --> 00:05:41,467
[AXE THUDS]

75
00:05:43,733 --> 00:05:45,567
[CHAIN RATTLES]

76
00:05:45,567 --> 00:05:48,633
[BREATHING HEAVILY, GRUNTS]

77
00:05:49,833 --> 00:05:56,800
[OMINOUS MUSIC CONTINUES]

78
00:06:04,833 --> 00:06:08,833
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

79
00:06:08,867 --> 00:06:15,800
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

80
00:06:30,833 --> 00:06:33,800
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

81
00:06:34,767 --> 00:06:35,867
Help!

82
00:06:36,933 --> 00:06:37,967
Help me!

83
00:06:38,833 --> 00:06:45,800
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

84
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,767
[GROANS]

85
00:07:00,867 --> 00:07:07,800
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

86
00:07:30,433 --> 00:07:37,433
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

87
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:52,167
[MUSIC TURNS OMINOUS]

88
00:07:59,567 --> 00:08:03,233
Wow, Kiko came all the way
here to find you.

89
00:08:03,233 --> 00:08:06,667
See how worried
your brother is about you?

90
00:08:06,667 --> 00:08:08,167
He came here
just to pick you up.

91
00:08:08,167 --> 00:08:13,200
[OMINOUS MUSIC CONTINUES]

92
00:08:29,967 --> 00:08:34,500
[LEON BREATHING HEAVILY]

93
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:41,133
[GRIM MUSIC PLAYING]

94
00:08:42,967 --> 00:08:44,033
[GRUNTS]

95
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:49,100
[GRUNTS]

96
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:55,933
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

97
00:08:58,133 --> 00:09:00,133
[MUSIC TURNS SUSPENSEFUL]

98
00:09:00,133 --> 00:09:03,667
[GRUNTS, COUGHS]

99
00:09:15,033 --> 00:09:16,800
[STAIRS CREAKING]

100
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:23,767
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

101
00:09:28,033 --> 00:09:30,067
[STAIRS CREAKING]

102
00:09:30,067 --> 00:09:34,933
[LEON GRUNTING]

103
00:09:36,267 --> 00:09:38,167
[GRUNTING CONTINUES]

104
00:09:38,167 --> 00:09:40,033
[PANTING]

105
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:41,933
[GRUNTS]

106
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:49,567
- [LEON GRUNTS, PANTS]
- [GATE CLANGS]

107
00:09:49,567 --> 00:09:55,633
[MUSIC TURNS GRIM]

108
00:09:55,633 --> 00:09:59,700
[GRUNTING]

109
00:10:02,867 --> 00:10:09,767
[MUSIC TURNS SUSPENSEFUL]

110
00:10:14,933 --> 00:10:15,867
Cheska.

111
00:10:16,633 --> 00:10:17,600
What's wrong?

112
00:10:19,033 --> 00:10:20,967
Nothing. I just...

113
00:10:22,300 --> 00:10:24,200
I just got a bad feeling.

114
00:10:27,067 --> 00:10:30,300
I don't know why, but I
suddenly feel nervous.

115
00:10:31,667 --> 00:10:33,067
That won't work on me.

116
00:10:33,667 --> 00:10:35,100
Come on, let's head back
to the hotel.

117
00:10:35,733 --> 00:10:37,200
I gave Kiko my word.

118
00:10:37,967 --> 00:10:39,967
Come on, let's go.

119
00:10:42,733 --> 00:10:49,633
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

120
00:10:53,667 --> 00:10:56,767
[MUSIC TURNS DARK]

121
00:10:56,767 --> 00:10:57,733
Who are you?

122
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:04,567
Where's my map?

123
00:11:05,067 --> 00:11:06,467
What map?

124
00:11:06,467 --> 00:11:08,600
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

125
00:11:08,633 --> 00:11:10,467
I don't know what
you're talking about!

126
00:11:10,467 --> 00:11:12,167
Give me my map!

127
00:11:12,167 --> 00:11:14,000
No, I don't have it!

128
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,567
[SANDRO] Stealing is wrong!

129
00:11:15,567 --> 00:11:17,167
I'll ask you again!

130
00:11:17,167 --> 00:11:18,300
Where's my map?!

131
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,300
I don't know!

132
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:21,000
- [GROWLS]
- [BLADE SWISHES]

133
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,133
[KIKO] Help!

134
00:11:22,467 --> 00:11:23,633
Help!

135
00:11:23,633 --> 00:11:28,633
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

136
00:11:28,633 --> 00:11:35,600
[GROANING IN PAIN]

137
00:11:43,633 --> 00:11:49,233
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

138
00:11:49,233 --> 00:11:50,367
[KIKO] Help!

139
00:11:52,467 --> 00:11:53,600
Help!

140
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,133
Help!

141
00:11:56,633 --> 00:11:58,200
[KIKO] Help!

142
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,133
Help!

143
00:12:04,233 --> 00:12:11,200
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

144
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:13,200
[MARTIN] Are we only
missing one more map?

145
00:12:13,633 --> 00:12:15,300
We'll find out once
Kiko returns,

146
00:12:15,333 --> 00:12:17,500
but I feel like
we're getting close now.

147
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:18,333
At least--

148
00:12:18,333 --> 00:12:20,567
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

149
00:12:20,567 --> 00:12:22,900
Speaking of Kiko,
he's calling right now.

150
00:12:24,667 --> 00:12:25,900
Kiko?

151
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:28,600
Brother, please help me!
Someone's chasing me!

152
00:12:29,233 --> 00:12:30,400
- [GIO]<i> Where are you, Kiko?!
</i>- [MARTIN] What's happening?

153
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,567
[MARTIN] Put it on speaker mode!

154
00:12:31,567 --> 00:12:32,900
Gio, hurry up!

155
00:12:33,167 --> 00:12:34,567
[KIKO] I don't know who he is!

156
00:12:34,567 --> 00:12:36,400
We're in the forest
behind the hotel!

157
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,533
[KIKO] He's asking me where--

158
00:12:37,533 --> 00:12:39,567
- [GIO]<i> What is he looking for?!
</i>- [SANDRO YELLING]

159
00:12:39,567 --> 00:12:40,933
- Kiko, respond!
- Kiko!

160
00:12:40,933 --> 00:12:42,300
Kiko!

161
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:45,300
Gio! Gio, hurry up! Let's move!

162
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:49,700
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

163
00:12:49,733 --> 00:12:53,733
- [GRUNTING]
- [BLADE SWISHES]

164
00:12:53,733 --> 00:12:58,733
[GROANING]

165
00:12:58,733 --> 00:13:02,700
- [SANDRO GRUNTING]
- [BLADE SWISHING]

166
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,167
[RAPHIE] Sir, what's going on?

167
00:13:07,167 --> 00:13:08,567
Kiko's in danger.
We need to help him!

168
00:13:08,567 --> 00:13:10,367
What? How could that happen?

169
00:13:10,633 --> 00:13:12,633
I don't know!
Let's just talk later.

170
00:13:12,633 --> 00:13:14,500
- I'll go with you, sir!
- No, Raphie! You can't.

171
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:15,533
Just call the police.

172
00:13:15,533 --> 00:13:17,367
[GIO] Tell Luna and her family
to be careful!

173
00:13:19,233 --> 00:13:20,633
[GROANING]

174
00:13:20,633 --> 00:13:22,233
[BODY THUDS]

175
00:13:22,267 --> 00:13:29,267
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

176
00:13:29,267 --> 00:13:31,433
Where's my map?

177
00:13:31,433 --> 00:13:33,167
I don't have a map.

178
00:13:33,167 --> 00:13:34,667
Please, please don't kill me.

179
00:13:34,667 --> 00:13:36,267
- [SANDRO] Where's my map?
- [KIKO WHIMPERS]

180
00:13:36,267 --> 00:13:39,667
Where is my map?!

181
00:13:39,667 --> 00:13:41,000
[KIKO WHIMPERING]

182
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,400
[LEON GROWLS]

183
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:44,667
- [BODY THUDS]
- [SANDRO GROANING IN PAIN]

184
00:13:44,667 --> 00:13:47,500
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

185
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,633
Leon?

186
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:50,733
- But how?
- We need to go!

187
00:13:50,733 --> 00:13:53,067
- Where?
- Just ask questions later!

188
00:13:53,267 --> 00:13:54,600
[SANDRO GROANING]

189
00:13:55,267 --> 00:13:56,400
[KIKO] Leon!

190
00:13:56,667 --> 00:13:58,000
Hurry up!

191
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:09,467
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

192
00:14:11,167 --> 00:14:12,667
- [GIO] Kiko!
- [MARTIN] Kiko!

193
00:14:12,667 --> 00:14:14,633
- Kiko!
- Kiko!

194
00:14:15,333 --> 00:14:16,467
Kiko!

195
00:14:17,333 --> 00:14:18,467
Kiko!

196
00:14:24,567 --> 00:14:25,700
Kiko!

197
00:14:26,167 --> 00:14:31,333
[PANTING]

198
00:14:31,367 --> 00:14:33,367
Come on! Hurry up!

199
00:14:33,367 --> 00:14:36,367
[LEON] Let's hide here.

200
00:14:36,367 --> 00:14:41,200
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

201
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,333
[GROANING IN PAIN]

202
00:14:47,267 --> 00:14:48,400
[PANTING]

203
00:14:49,333 --> 00:14:50,500
You should go ahead.

204
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:52,833
Your siblings are
waiting for you.

205
00:14:52,833 --> 00:14:54,667
- I won't leave you here.
- [SANDRO YELLS]

206
00:14:54,667 --> 00:14:55,667
[PANTING]

207
00:14:55,667 --> 00:14:56,667
[LEON SHUSHES]

208
00:14:56,667 --> 00:14:58,433
- [SANDRO GROANING IN PAIN]
- [WHIMPERING]

209
00:14:58,433 --> 00:15:05,367
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

210
00:15:20,433 --> 00:15:27,400
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

211
00:15:40,467 --> 00:15:41,567
[SANDRO GROANING]

212
00:15:42,467 --> 00:15:47,300
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

213
00:15:47,300 --> 00:15:54,300
[LEON BREATHING HEAVILY]

214
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:57,267
Please escape now or
both of us will die here.

215
00:15:57,267 --> 00:15:59,667
I won't leave you behind!

216
00:15:59,667 --> 00:16:01,667
Please, just go!

217
00:16:01,667 --> 00:16:05,500
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

218
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:07,367
He's Sandro.

219
00:16:07,367 --> 00:16:09,667
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

220
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:11,300
What? S-Sandro?

221
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:12,700
Who is that?

222
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:15,533
Whatever happens to us,

223
00:16:15,533 --> 00:16:17,367
you need to tell them...

224
00:16:17,367 --> 00:16:20,333
- [COUGHING]
- Leon...

225
00:16:20,533 --> 00:16:24,600
You need to tell them
that Sandro's alive.

226
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:27,600
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

227
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,400
We'll get out of here together.

228
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,367
Come on. Let's go.

229
00:16:31,367 --> 00:16:37,667
[LEON GROANING IN PAIN]

230
00:16:37,667 --> 00:16:41,667
- [STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [LEON PANTING]

231
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:43,700
- [BLADE SWISHES]
- [BODY THUDS]

232
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:45,233
Leon!

233
00:16:45,233 --> 00:16:47,233
Kiko, go!

234
00:16:47,233 --> 00:16:48,467
Kiko, go ahead!

235
00:16:48,467 --> 00:16:51,467
[LEON] You should escape!
Leave me!

236
00:16:51,467 --> 00:16:58,433
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

237
00:17:00,833 --> 00:17:04,600
[BOTH GRUNTING]

238
00:17:04,600 --> 00:17:10,833
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

239
00:17:10,833 --> 00:17:11,833
[GRUNTING]

240
00:17:13,067 --> 00:17:14,100
Leon!

241
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:16,067
Kiko, run!

242
00:17:16,100 --> 00:17:17,667
Kiko, hurry!

243
00:17:17,667 --> 00:17:19,833
[LEON] Escape now! Go!

244
00:17:19,833 --> 00:17:20,733
[LEON GRUNTS]

245
00:17:20,733 --> 00:17:24,133
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

246
00:17:24,133 --> 00:17:25,033
Come on!

247
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:27,033
What, Raphie?!

248
00:17:27,033 --> 00:17:28,667
Is that true?

249
00:17:29,567 --> 00:17:32,000
Okay. Just keep us posted.

250
00:17:33,733 --> 00:17:35,533
Luna, what is it?
What happened?

251
00:17:36,533 --> 00:17:38,500
Raphie said we should
be careful.

252
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:39,767
[JADE] Why? What's
the problem this time?

253
00:17:40,833 --> 00:17:42,033
Kiko's in danger.

254
00:17:42,033 --> 00:17:43,000
What?!

255
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,433
[JUSTIN] What do you mean
he's in danger?

256
00:17:44,433 --> 00:17:45,433
I was just talking to him.

257
00:17:45,733 --> 00:17:48,133
How'd you talk to him?

258
00:17:48,167 --> 00:17:50,067
He said someone's
chasing him in the woods.

259
00:17:50,867 --> 00:17:51,867
Oh, shi--

260
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:53,733
[LUNA] What?

261
00:17:53,733 --> 00:17:55,033
Justin!

262
00:17:55,033 --> 00:17:57,200
I was supposed to meet him there
because of Cheska and Trixie.

263
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:59,967
What? They haven't
gone home yet?

264
00:17:59,967 --> 00:18:01,933
Are they also in the woods?

265
00:18:01,933 --> 00:18:03,800
We were about
to go back to the hotel.

266
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:05,567
But they said they need
to drop by Sari's house

267
00:18:05,567 --> 00:18:07,033
to get their things.

268
00:18:07,033 --> 00:18:09,000
I texted Kiko
to pick them up there.

269
00:18:09,833 --> 00:18:11,467
So that's why he hasn't replied.

270
00:18:12,567 --> 00:18:14,000
T-This can't be.

271
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:14,967
Kiko needs me.

272
00:18:14,967 --> 00:18:17,500
- I need to go.
- Jade, are you crazy?!

273
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:19,633
Gio told us to be careful,

274
00:18:19,633 --> 00:18:21,100
and you want to go there?

275
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:22,667
But what about Kiko?

276
00:18:23,233 --> 00:18:25,033
Raphie already called
the police.

277
00:18:25,033 --> 00:18:27,467
Gio and Martin
are looking for Kiko.

278
00:18:27,467 --> 00:18:29,100
They won't let something bad
happen to Kiko, Jade.

279
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:35,600
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

280
00:18:37,100 --> 00:18:38,700
[LEON] Kiko, go!

281
00:18:38,700 --> 00:18:40,533
[BOTH GRUNTING]

282
00:18:43,633 --> 00:18:44,733
Kiko, run!

283
00:18:44,733 --> 00:18:46,067
- [GRUNTING]
- [SLASHING]

284
00:18:46,067 --> 00:18:48,200
[GRUNTING]

285
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:52,900
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

286
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:55,167
[GRUNTING]

287
00:18:56,567 --> 00:18:57,600
[GROANS IN PAIN]

288
00:18:58,100 --> 00:19:01,000
[GRUNTING]

289
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:01,967
[FLESH SQUELCHES]

290
00:19:01,967 --> 00:19:08,967
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

291
00:19:18,733 --> 00:19:20,633
[SANDRO PANTS]

292
00:19:23,167 --> 00:19:29,767
[DARK MUSIC CONTINUES]

293
00:19:41,133 --> 00:19:47,333
[GRIM MUSIC PLAYING]

294
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:51,033
[MARTIN] Leon!

295
00:19:52,967 --> 00:19:54,367
Leon, wake up.

296
00:19:54,367 --> 00:19:56,200
Leon! Leon, wake up!

297
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,367
[GIO] Kiko!

298
00:19:57,367 --> 00:20:00,200
[CRYING]

299
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,367
Kiko!

300
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,400
[MARTIN] Leon?

301
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,767
Leon!

302
00:20:03,767 --> 00:20:04,867
Leon.

303
00:20:05,167 --> 00:20:06,300
Come on.

304
00:20:06,300 --> 00:20:08,667
Come on, Leon. Please.

305
00:20:08,667 --> 00:20:13,067
[GRIM MUSIC CONTINUES]

306
00:20:13,067 --> 00:20:14,200
Kiko?

307
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,100
Kiko?

308
00:20:20,833 --> 00:20:22,100
Kiko!

309
00:20:25,233 --> 00:20:26,367
[CRYING]

310
00:20:26,367 --> 00:20:27,700
Kiko!

311
00:20:28,067 --> 00:20:31,300
[GRIM MUSIC CONTINUES]

312
00:20:31,300 --> 00:20:38,267
[SOBBING]

313
00:20:38,700 --> 00:20:40,633
Leon, wake up!

314
00:20:41,767 --> 00:20:44,033
[MARTIN] Leon! Leon!

315
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,733
[GIO] Kiko!

316
00:20:47,833 --> 00:20:49,067
Kiko!

317
00:20:49,067 --> 00:20:50,900
- [SOBBING]
- Kiko!

318
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:52,067
Kiko!

319
00:20:52,067 --> 00:20:58,200
[SOBBING CONTINUES]

320
00:20:58,667 --> 00:20:59,567
[GIO] Kiko...

321
00:20:59,567 --> 00:21:01,267
[MARTIN] Kiko,
stay with us, please!

322
00:21:02,067 --> 00:21:05,667
Nurse! I'm begging you!
Help my brother!

323
00:21:05,667 --> 00:21:09,067
Don't let go, Kiko!
Hold on, Kiko!

324
00:21:09,100 --> 00:21:11,233
- Kiko, please!
- Kiko!

325
00:21:11,233 --> 00:21:12,400
Kiko!

326
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:16,000
[GIO] Nurse, take care
of my brother. Kiko!

327
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,400
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

328
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,733
[KIKO] Brother...

329
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:23,233
[LUNA] Brother, please hold on!

330
00:21:23,233 --> 00:21:26,233
- Nurse, please help my brother!
- Brother, stay with us!

331
00:21:26,233 --> 00:21:28,933
- Leon, please!
- Brother! Brother!

332
00:21:28,933 --> 00:21:30,067
- [JUSTIN] We're here now!
- [SOBBING]

333
00:21:30,067 --> 00:21:31,233
[JUSTIN] You're going
to survive this!

334
00:21:31,233 --> 00:21:34,233
- Brother!
- [WAILING]

335
00:21:34,233 --> 00:21:36,467
[MOROSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

336
00:21:36,467 --> 00:21:37,833
[LEON] Luna...

337
00:21:37,833 --> 00:21:39,000
<i> Justin...</i>

338
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,100
<i> Jade...</i>

339
00:21:40,100 --> 00:21:43,700
<i>He went to the forest
because of me, Martin.</i>

340
00:21:44,867 --> 00:21:47,000
[MARTIN] Because
you didn't obey me,

341
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,367
<i> look at what happened.</i>

342
00:21:48,933 --> 00:21:49,900
<i> Brother...</i>

343
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:52,933
<i>Can't you do anything
to save him?!</i>

344
00:21:52,933 --> 00:21:54,233
<i> Mama...</i>

345
00:21:54,233 --> 00:21:57,333
[FLAT LINE]

346
00:21:57,333 --> 00:21:59,467
<i> We did everything we could.</i>

347
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,767
[HENRI] Something's wrong.

348
00:22:04,767 --> 00:22:06,767
<i>This wasn't done by
someone who's not from here.</i>

349
00:22:06,767 --> 00:22:10,100
[FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]
